WEBVTT

00:00.010 --> 00:01.600
They took Lena.

00:01.819 --> 00:03.500
Who took her?

00:03.840 --> 00:05.240
DCFS.

00:05.300 --> 00:06.969
We'll get her back.

00:06.970 --> 00:09.080
I-I want to set up a
few holding companies.

00:09.100 --> 00:11.969
You know, a couple layers of papers,

00:11.970 --> 00:13.720
make it tough to track.

00:13.760 --> 00:15.770
I'm gonna have to report
this back to Smurf.

00:15.780 --> 00:16.790
No, you won't.

00:16.860 --> 00:18.060
Why not?

00:18.130 --> 00:20.160
Because you're smarter than that.

00:20.220 --> 00:22.329
You sicko bitch! You're done!

00:24.400 --> 00:25.770
Aah!

00:26.940 --> 00:29.220
- I hit Marco, man.
- Where's Pope?

00:29.260 --> 00:32.220
What happened to Marco was unfortunate.

00:32.340 --> 00:34.210
Where's my son, Lucy?

00:34.250 --> 00:35.300
You want Pope?

00:35.320 --> 00:38.400
Tell me you had Baz killed.

00:38.420 --> 00:40.980
